## If You Need to Execute Tests

Use `-Dsuites=` (not `-Dtest=`) for scalatest-maven-plugin:

```bash
# Run all doc tests
mvn test -Dsuites='com.databricks.labs.gbx.docs.*' 2>&1 | tee test-logs/doc-tests-exec-$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S).log

# Run specific doc test
mvn test -Dsuites=com.databricks.labs.gbx.docs.advanced.CustomUdfsDocTest
```

